"content":"V2-IO-11  回写 18/19/20、engine-boundaries、AGENTS 过期句","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":114,"content":"V2-IO-12  验收勾选需求 §6；删除引擎内遗留 IO 实现文件（无兼容转发壳）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":115,"content":"```","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":116,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":117,"content":"`group: order`：严格按表取 ⬜。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":118,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":119,"content":"> **gbx 表解析注意：** 任务单元格勿写英文 `status`、勿写「状态」子串。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":120,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":121,"content":"### 0.3 全批声明","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":122,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":123,"content":"```text","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":124,"content":"行为目标：本机存取行为 ≡ 迁前；引擎包无 fs/sqlite 实现","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":125,"content":"verify：quality:engine + quality:studio","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":126,"content":"max_rounds：80","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":127,"content":"```","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":128,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":129,"content":"---","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":130,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":131,"content":"## 1. 任务表","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":132,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":133,"content":"| 状态 | ID | 任务 | verify |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":134,"content":"|------|-----|------|--------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":135,"content":"| ✅ | V2-IO-1 | **口径确认**：对照需求 §2–§4 与技术设计 23；缺口只补文档不写业务代码 | true |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":136,"content":"| ✅ | V2-IO-2 | **引擎 Port 面**：导出 Content/Profile/EngineLog（+既有 Memory）类型；`createEngineHost` 注入选项与缺省策略钉死 | npm run quality:engine |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":137,"content":"| ✅ | V2-IO-3 | **engineIOModule 骨架**：`apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/` 目录职责说明；禁止 Client 引用 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":138,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-IO-4 | **Memory 迁出**：`sqliteMemoryPort` → engineIOModule；引擎测用假 Port 或测试注入 | npm run quality:engine |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":139,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-IO-5 | **Profile 迁出**：读/写薄 Profile 经 ProfilePort；删除引擎内直写 fs 真源 | npm run quality:engine |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":140,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-IO-6 | **Content/Workspace 迁出**：loadWorkspace 扫描/读 JSON 经 ContentPort | npm run quality:engine |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":141,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-IO-7 | **EngineLog 迁出**：jsonl 追加/切片经 LogPort | npm run quality:engine |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":142,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-IO-8 | **validate 读盘解耦**：validatePackage（及同类）不直接 `readFile`；由 Port 提供包内容 | npm run quality:engine |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":143,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-IO-9 | **装配**：StudioV2 创建 engineIOModule Ports 并注入 Host（API/单例处） | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":144,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-IO-10 | **门禁与回归**：Client 禁 engineIOModule；host/memory/validation 测绿；隔离 005/020 仍为 0 | npm run quality:engine · npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":145,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-IO-11 | **文档收口**：18/19/20、engine-boundaries、AGENTS、README 用法与 23 交叉链接一致 | true |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":146,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-IO-12 | **删遗留实现 + 验收**：引擎包无 IO 实现残留/转发壳；需求 §6 勾选 | npm run quality:engine · npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":147,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":148,"content":"---","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":149,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":150,"content":"## 2. 批次出口（每批结束后）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":151,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":152,"content":"- 本批任务均为 ✅","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":153,"content":"- 任务 `verify` / `verify_default` exit 0","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":154,"content":"- Reviewer：`reviews/latest.json` 中 `blocker=0` 且 `critical=0`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":155,"content":"- 无 hard_stop 命中","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":156,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":157,"content":"---","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":158,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":159,"content":"## 3. 人工验收（批末）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":160,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":161,"content":"- [ ] 本机 Studio 读包 / 存 Profile / Memory / 日志路径与迁前一致","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":162,"content":"- [ ] 引擎包可被「无 fs 的测试宿主」仅靠假 Port 跑通核心单测","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":163,"content":"- [ ] 未引入浏览器本地 IO","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true}]}],"totalLines":99,"totalMatchedLines":2,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-8151a541-c746-48b5-9205-046e670dee7