torySave、Memory 或 StoryPackage 真源。\\n- store 不直接读写磁盘。\\n- store 不直接导入引擎写口。\\n\\n### 4.4 utils\\n\\n`src/utils/` 放真正跨页面复用的工具。\\n\\n```text\\nsrc/utils/\\n  ajaxProxy/\\n  ajaxHelper/\\n  hooks/\\n  helper/\\n  config.ts\\n  utils.ts\\n```\\n\\n规则：\\n\\n- `ajaxProxy/`：按模块拆分的请求纯函数，例如故事包、资源、调试器。\\n- `ajaxHelper/`：请求器、错误归一、响应解析等基础设施。\\n- `hooks/`：全局复用 hooks。\\n- `helper/`：全局纯函数，按主题拆文件。\\n- `config.ts`：环境变量和运行配置唯一出口。\\n- `utils.ts`：只允许少量无业务含义的全局小函数；一旦变长必须拆入 `helper/`。\\n\\n`utils/` 不是垃圾桶。任何带业务语义的东西必须优先进入页面 bis、页面组件目录或 `typeFiles/`。\\n\\n### 4.5 commonUiComponents\\n\\n`src/common [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":188,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\"\\n\\nV2-IO-3 requires a README documenting the Client ban. The structure gate must treat `engineIOModule` as Server-only. I need to verify whether STUDIO-STRUCT-020 already blocks Client imports of Server paths, or only the reverse. I will review the import boundary checks carefully.\",\"session_id\":\"3dd39215-a74e-4194-ba37-c53921ec7914\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784781260160}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":199,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\"Starting V2-IO-3 by \",\"session_id\":\"3dd39215-a74e-4194-ba37-c53921ec7914\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784781262719}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":259,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\" createEngineIOPorts.ts\",\"session_id\":\"3dd39215-a74e-4194-ba37-c53921ec7914\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784781271327}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":281,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\" that detector. V2-IO-3\",\"session_id\":\"3dd39215-a74e-4194-ba37-c53921ec7914\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784781274960}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":306,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\" up