契约，不内置 better-sqlite3。  \",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false}]},{\"file\":\"./docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md\",\"matches\":[{\"lineNumber\":7,\"content\":\"**存取：** Host 经注入的 Content / Profile / Memory / EngineLog Port 访问工作区；磁盘布局由 IO 模块解释。本机实现见 `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`（详见 [23](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)）。\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":17,\"content\":\"  → createEngineIOPorts(dataRoot)     # Studio：engineIOModule\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false}]},{\"file\":\"./.cursor/rules/engine-boundaries.mdc\",\"matches\":[{\"lineNumber\":23,\"content\":\"- **存取：** 经 Port 注入（见技术设计 [23](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)）；**禁止**本包内长期保留 `node:fs` / `better-sqlite3` 实现。本机实现落在 `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`。\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false}]},{\"file\":\"./docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/00-技术设计索引.md\",\"matches\":[{\"lineNumber\":19,\"content\":\"| [23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md) | **存取 Port 协议；本机 IO 在 studioV2/engineIOModule；禁引擎内 fs/sqlite 实现** |\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false}]},{\"file\":\"./docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/引擎存取Port抽象_需求.md\",\"matches\":[{\"lineNumber\":4,\"content\":\"> **性质：** 将引擎与具体存储 IO **程序拆清 + 物理拆清**：引擎只暴露存/取协议（callback / Port）；现网 JSON+fs+SQLite 实现迁出到 Studio V2 `engineIOModule`。  \",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":22,\"content\":\"  · 落入 apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/（本机 Studio 默认适配）\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":45,\"content\":\"| Client↔Server 隔离 | `engineIOModule` = Server 区；Client 禁止 import |\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":57,\"content\":\"apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":65,\"content\":\"**铁律：** 独立性优先于 DRY；引擎不 import `engineIOModule`；`engineIOModule` 可依赖引擎 **类型/契约**（及引擎 schema 解析若需要），但引擎核心不得反向依赖 Studio。\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":84,\"content\":\"## 4. 物理迁出清单（从引擎迁到 engineIOModule）\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":90,\"content\":\"| `memory/sqliteMemoryPort.ts` | `engineIOModule` 内 Sqlite Memory 实现 |\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":103,\"content\":\"2. **禁止** Client / `pageComponents` / `bis` / `typeFiles` import `engineIOModule`。  \",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":104,\"content\":\"3. 门禁：延续 `STUDIO-STRUCT-005/020`；必要时增加「Client 禁 `engineIOModule`」检测。  \",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":105,\"content\":\"4. Vitest：引擎测用内存假 Port；IO 模块单测可放 `apps/studioV2/tests/` 或 `engineIOModule` 旁约定 `tests/`（不进 Client bundle）。\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":112,\"content\":\"- [ ] `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/` 存在且承载现网本机 IO\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":116,\"content\":\"- [ ] Client 无法 import `engineIOModule`\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false}]}],\"totalLines\":108,\"totalMatchedLines\":108,\"clientTruncated\":false,\"ripgrepTruncated\":false}}}}}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-a2b9ca75-7162-43db-bb17-bac890d28d88-7\\nfc_9fb7f027-45fb-9ed4-b450-166efe759aec_2\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784781235918\",\"completedAtMs\":\"1784781236457\"},\"model_call_id\":\"4eac2f80-35c0-431c-80ce-85fec7e20846-2-rrv3\",\"session_id\":\"3dd39215-a74e-4194-ba37-c53921ec7914\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784781236454}\n80:{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-0dfaac5a-d8ca-473b-966e-338f5ceb7bce-12\\nfc_7e891c96-6e30-961c-819f-a89faa40e58e_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"shellToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"command\":\"ls -la apps/studioV2/ | head -50; ls -la apps/studioV2/engineIOModule 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"engineIOModule does not exist\\\"\",\"workingDirectory\":\"\",\"timeout\":30000,\"toolCallId\":\"call-0dfaac5a-d8ca-473b-966e-338f5ceb7bce-12\\