{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-4f386637-9579-4785-b055-f5b82aff6172-47\nfc_fcbbe74e-173c-9921-b3d5-ee52ecd3c43f_3","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/engine-code-quality.mdc","limit":30},"result":{"success":{"content":"---\ndescription: 引擎代码结构、注释与高风险落点硬规则（本库门禁真源）\nglobs:\n  - packages/rpg-engine/**\n  - scripts/engine-quality/**\nalwaysApply: false\n---\n\n# 引擎代码质量规则\n\n本规则适用于 `packages/rpg-engine` 与引擎质量门禁脚本。机器门禁入口为本库根命令 `npm run quality:engine`（**不在** `general-batch-exe` skill 内实现结构检查）。\n\n与 [engine-boundaries.mdc](./engine-boundaries.mdc)（纯度 / Host 边界）互补：本文件管可读性、规模止血与高风险落点声明。\n\n## 必须执行\n\n- 公共契约、Port、状态转换、幂等 / 事务 / 时序逻辑必须有意图注释或 JSDoc（解释为什么、约束或副作用，禁止复述代码）。\n- `createEngineHost` / Host 装配层只做装配与会话协调，不新增可独立命名的领域算法；新算法落到 `runtime/`、`schedule/`、`workspace/` 等明确模块。\n- `effectExecutor` 只做 Effect 调度；复杂 effect 委派 handler / 领域服务，禁止继续无边界堆叠。\n- Schedule once、recurring、clock、card reference、chapter cleanup 是可分离职责；禁止把新规则只塞进 `scheduleTick.ts`。\n- 高风险功能任务必须在执行索引中声明：目标模块、允许修改、禁止落点、状态不变量、负向测试、`verify: npm run quality:engine`、结构预算。\n- 新文件 / 新函数执行硬上限；已超限遗留文件以 `scripts/engine-quality/engine-quality-baseline.json` 止血——触碰后受控指标不得净增长。\n- `eslint-disable`、`@ts-ignore`、`@ts-expect-error`、门禁豁免必须在同处写明原因；临时豁免写清退出条件。\n- 引擎合并前必须通过 `npm run quality:engine`；不得以人工承诺替代机器门禁。\n\n## 阈值（与 check:engine-structure 一致）\n\n| 对象 | 告警线 | 硬上限 |\n|---|---:|---:|\n| 普通引擎源码文件 | 350 | 500 |","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":44,"fileSize":2496,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/engine-code-quality.mdc","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":30},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-4f386637-9579-4785-b055-f5b82aff6172-47\nfc_fcbbe74e-173c-9921-b3d5-ee52ecd3c43f_3","startedAtMs":"1784781535706","completedAtMs":"1784781535859"},"model_call_id":"2310601a-1e8e-4d84-91ad-c4a6d394ccba-9-c9yi","session_id":"d63bd641-12cd-4e19-ad56-02